
1) Make a AWS application load balancer under EC2 category
2) Create new Target group for the load balancing
  a) Target group should have target Lambda
3) Add new HTTP(80) or HTTPs(443) listner in the application load balancer
4) Add new rule for the context based routing - ()
  a) Route based on the PATH
  b) Forward the request to Target group
  
5) Load balancer should forward the request the Lambda
6) Check the Cloud watch -> Log groups ()
7) Select the Lambda and view if the request is received over the Lambda


Note: The AWS application load balancer should respond with specific attributes, and BODY should be String not any other object
